The paper discusses a new algorithm for collaborative editing of XML data that ensures scalable consistency of replicated data. This topic falls under the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) sub-category, which is the most likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with data structures (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB) which are also likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL) as it presents a new approach for handling all the XML editing aspects.
